<h2>Thank you for joing the Helping Central Texas community!</h2>

<p>You have successfully signed up with the email address <%= @user.email %></p>

<h3>For Those In Need:</h3>
<p>
  - Please <%= link_to "update your profile", edit_user_registration_url, target: "_blank" %> and add your requests. Don't worry if your needs aren't on the list, just select what is closest and you'll have the option to add a note when you find a matching resource.
</p>
<p>
  - <%= link_to "Browse the resource list", projects_url, target: "_blank" %> daily and see if anything you need is being offered.
</p>
<h3>For Providers:</h3>
<p>
  - <%= link_to "Update your profile.", edit_user_registration_url, target: "_blank" %> 
  Please complete your profile, and leave the 'resources needed' field blank if you are not in need of anything yourself, but you 
  can also select any resources you may need if you wish to request aid as well.
</p>
<p>
  -  <%= link_to "Create your first resource here", new_project_url, target: "_blank" %> and add the details for your offered resource(s).
</p>
<p>
  - Need aid? <%= link_to "Browse the resource list", projects_url, target: "_blank" %>  and see if anything you need is being offered.
</p>

<p>Thank you for doing your part to help our communities!<br/>
  The Helping Central Texas team</p>
